---
// About Section - Sanjay D's Story
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-background to-background/95">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">
        About <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent">Me</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        My journey from curiosity to creation
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Story Content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-muted-foreground">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Hey! I'm Sanjay, a 22-year-old full-stack developer who discovered the magic of coding during my engineering journey at Sri Krishna College of Technology.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            My programming adventure began when I first wrote HTML and CSS to create a house interior design website. Seeing static code transform into a beautiful, responsive interface felt like digital wizardry! That moment sparked my curiosity to dive deeper into the world of web development.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            What drives me is the challenge of turning complex problems into elegant solutions. Whether it's building secure authentication systems with JWT or creating smooth user interfaces, I approach each project with curiosity and determination to craft something meaningful.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Currently maintaining a strong 7.4 GPA while gaining hands-on experience through internships, I'm always eager to learn new technologies and contribute to projects that make a difference.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <div class="pt-6">
          <a 
            href="#contact" 
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-primary-foreground rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-primary/90 hover:scale-105"
          >
            Let's Connect
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Enhanced Image -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="relative group">
          <img 
            src="/lovable-uploads/224479e8-d491-449c-a9f8-ccb0b9c8aedb.png"
            alt="Sanjay D - Full Stack Developer"
            class="w-80 h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/20 to-accent/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 via-accent/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-3xl blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
